Player-Mpg123 version 0.01
==========================

This component allows for manipulation of the mpg123 player from
within the POE environment.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

1. the POE state engine
2. the "mpg123" player

